E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Clay, I know you take your Road Captaining responsibilities real serious so can you bring me a Slam Van?
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~Clay，我知道你是个尽职尽责的行车长，所以你可以给我送一辆Slam Van吗？

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Clay, man, I really need a bike. Can you help me out?
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~Clay，哥们，我真的很需要一辆摩托。你能帮帮我吗？

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~I'm a coming, brother. You just wait there.
E1FCC4_ACT_E1C_GETCALL_SPEC_THANKSA
~z~Yeah, we'll come, man. Just don't get us killed, alright?
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~好的，咱们来了，哥们。你可别是叫弟兄们来送死啊？

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Clayton, dude, how bout bringing a Slam Van out to me?
~z~Clayton, I'd like to have a ride on a Lycan. Is that cool with you?
~z~Hey there, Road Captain. I wanna try some of that Jap Scrap. Can you bring me a Hakuchou?
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~嘿，行车长。我想开开日本车。你能给我送辆Hakuchou吗？

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~On our way, man.
E1FCC4_ACT_E1C_CALL_REQ_SPEC_ZOMBIEA
~z~Anything for the Chapter President, man.
E1FCC4_ACT_E1C_CALL_REQ_SPEC_INNOVATIONA
~z~Brothers for life, man.
~z~Shit, dude, I'm sorry. I can't help you right now. I might be able to source something in a little while though.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~妈的，老兄，真抱歉。我现在帮不了你。过段时间我可能能弄到几辆。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Clayton! Man, can you bring me some vehicular assistance?
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~Clayton！哥们，你能给我支援一辆车吗？

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Okay, man. I'll remember this shit when you next go O.T.B.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~好吧，哥们。下次你摔个狗啃泥的时候我会记着这事的。

E1FCC4A.original: E1FCC4_ACT_E1C_CALL_REQ_SPEC_HELLFURYA
~z~Clayton, I could do with you and Terry's company.
~z~Clay, man, can you bring me a Revenant?
~z~So much for brotherhood, man. Thanks.
E1FCC4_ACT_E1C_GETCALL_HOSP_NOA
~z~You're the best fucking Road Captain this club's seen, man. Can you bring me some wheels, dude?
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~你真他妈是帮里最牛逼的行车长，哥们。能给我送辆车吗，老兄？

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~You know I'd love nothing more than to ride over to you and be left on the side of the road, but I can't help you at this second.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~你也知道我最喜欢骑车送给你然后被晾在路边了，但我现在真的帮不了你。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Listen Clayton, I'm in dire need of a Diabolus. Can you assist a brother?
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~听着，Clayton，我急需一辆Diabolus。你能帮兄弟一把吗？

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Okay dokey, brother. On my way.
E1FCC4_ACT_CALL_REQ_SPEC_YESA
~z~Hey man, can my Road Captain bring me a Hellfury?
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~嘿哥们，咱的行车长能不能送辆Hellfury过来？

E1FCC4A.original: E1FCC4_ACT_CALL_HOSP_CANCEL_HILIKEA
E1FCC4_ACT_GETCALL_HOSP_REJ_HILIKEA
~z~Clay, man, can you get me a Bati 800, man?
~z~Hey dude, can you find a Hexer for me to ride on?
~z~Clayton, I'm sorry but something came up. I can't come to the hospital.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~Clayton，我很抱歉，突然有点事，我来不了医院了。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~My man, Clay, you got a Diabolus in that garage of yours? I'd sure like to ride one.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~好哥们，Clay，你车库里有Diabolus吗？我需要一辆来骑。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Sounds like you looking for trouble, Johnny. We'll be there.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~听起来你遇到麻烦了，Johnny。咱们来了。

E1FCC4A.original: E1FCC4_ACT_CALL_HOSP_CANCEL_LOLIKEA
E1FCC4_ACT_CALL_REQ_BACKUP_YESA
~z~Clayton, man. If you got the time I'd really like you to bring me a Hellfury.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~Clayton，哥们。要是你有空的话，我希望你能给我送辆Hellfury。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Road Captain. I'm in need of a Bati 800. Can you accommodate?
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~行车长，我需要一辆Bati 800。你能弄到吗？

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Johnny, man, I was thinking. I should probably bring you a bike if you ever need one. Just gimme a call.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~Johnny，好哥们。我正在想，要是你需要车的话，我可以给你整一辆。给我打电话就行。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Jonathan, the meat mechanics are letting me out. Will you come get me?
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~Jonathan，血肉机械师让我出院了。你能来接我吗？

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Real sympathetic individual you are, John.
E1FCC4_ACT_E1C_CALL_HOSP_CANCELA
E1FCC4_ACT_GETCALL_HOSP_ACCEPTEDA
E1FCC4_ACT_CALL_REQ_HACK
~z~You lucky these nurses are hot, you one way son of a bitch. Later on.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~这些护士都很性感，算你这臭逼走运。再见。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Clay, man, let's ride in a pack. Get Terry and come meet me.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~Clay，哥们。咱们组团出去吧。叫上Terry来找我。

E1FCC4A.original: E1FCC4_ACT_GETCALL_HOSP_ASKA
E1FCC4_ACT_CALL_REQ_BACKUP_NOA
~z~Sorry, man. You gonna have to handle anything that comes along by yourself.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~对不起，哥们。待会儿遇到什么你都得自己解决了。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Clay, man, can you bring me an Innovation bike?
~z~Dude, where you at? Can you get Terry and come and meet me?
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~老兄，你在哪呢？能叫上Terry来找我吗？

E1FCC4A.original: E1FCC4_ACT_CALL_HOSP_CANCEL_MEDLIKEA
~z~Okay, man. I'll be out soon.
~z~Shit, man, you gonna have to handle it yourself. We're busy as hell.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~妈的，哥们，只能你自己解决了，我俩忙死了。

E1FCC4A.original: E1FCC4_ACT_E1C_CALL_REQ_SPEC_HEXERA
E1FCC4_ACT_CALL_REQ_BATI
E1FCC4_ACT_E1C_CALL_REQ_BACKUPA
~z~Clayton. How bout you and Terrence come and keep me company?
~z~Okay, man, we'll be with you soon.
~z~Clay, I'm thinking I'd look baddass on a Zombie B. How bout you bring me one?
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~Clay，我在想我骑上Zombie B会不会很拉风。能给我整一辆吗？

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Can't help you right now, man. We're tied up in our own shit.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~现在帮不了你，哥们。我们自己都忙不开。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~What kind of Road Captain am I? I can't even help you right now. Sorry, bro.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~我现在连你都帮不了，算啥行车长？对不起，兄弟。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Glad you got my back, brother. Enjoy the important shit you got on.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~谢谢你挺我啊，兄弟。你忙你的要紧事去吧。

E1FCC4A.original: E1FCC4_ACT_E1C_GETCALL_HOSP_YESA
E1FCC4_ACT_GETCALL_HOSP_REJ_LOLIKEA
E1FCC4_ACT_GETCALL_SPECA
~z~Okay, man, okay. I'm bringing it to you.
~z~Yo amigo, have you got a Zombie B to hand? I'd really like one of them bikes.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~哟，朋友，你手头有Zombie B吗？我很想整一辆来骑。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Shit, man. I'm sorry. We're kind of busy.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~妈的，哥们。抱歉了，我俩现在有点忙。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~I hate to disappoint a man as desperate as you, but you're gonna have to jack your own bike.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~我不想再给你浇一盆凉水，但你要的车得自己去抢了。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Johnny K. They stitched me up, man. I need a ride.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~Johnny K，我出院了，哥们。需要人来接。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Clay, my brother, do you reckon you could equip me with a Hexer, maybe?
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~Clay，好兄弟，能不能给我整辆Hexer过来？

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Shit, Johnny. Now I got to use more of my damn minutes on a call to Terry. Goodbye.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~妈的，Johnny。现在我他妈又得花点时间给Terry打电话了。再见。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Amigo. It'd feel good to have you and Terry by my side right now.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~朋友，要是现在你和Terry能在我旁边的话就很舒服了。

E1FCC4A.original: E1FCC4_ACT_E1C_CALL_REQ_SPEC_DIABOLUSA
E1FCC4_ACT_E1C_CALL_REQ_SPEC_LYCANA
~z~Clayton, man, I'm sorry. You best call one of the others. This brother's busy.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~Clayton，哥们，真抱歉。你还是找别人吧，兄弟我很忙。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Shit, Johnny, you sure are demanding. I'm on my way.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~妈的，Johnny，你要求真多啊。我在路上了。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Dude, can you and Terry get over to me? I'd like you here.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~老兄，你和Terry能来我这吗？我想你俩过来。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~That's cool, man. I'll give Terry a call.
~z~Amigo, I'm in need of some transport. You couldn't assist, could ya?
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~朋友，我需要辆车。你现在有空帮我吗？

E1FCC4A.original: E1FCC4_ACT_E1C_CALL_REQ_SPEC_GENERALA
~z~Clay brother, can you bring me over a Double? Thanks.
~z~Clay, man, you and Terry wanna ride with me?
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~Clay，哥们，你和Terry想跟我一起骑车吗？

E1FCC4A.original: E1FCC4_ACT_E1C_CALL_REQ_SPEC_REVENANTA
~z~Okay, man. I'll make another call.
E1FCC4_ACT_E1C_CALL_REQ_SPEC_SLAMVANA
~z~I sure do got one of those. I'll bring it out.
~z~When a brother needs backup, that's what he gets. Lost MC for life, man.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~兄弟有难，八方支援。失落帮万岁，哥们。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Sure, brother. I might just get a hot momma to come pick me up.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~好啊，兄弟。也许我应该找个辣妈来接我。

E1FCC4A.original: E1FCC4_ACT_GETCALL_HOSP_REJ_MEDLIKEA
~z~You're going to have to call one of the others, Clay. I got something else to handle.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~你还是问问别人吧，Clay，我还有事情要忙。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Glad to see you taking your club responsibilities seriously. Thanks, brother.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~看到你勤勤恳恳地给帮里做事，我很高兴。谢了，兄弟。

E1FCC4A.original: E1FCC4_ACT_CALL_REQ_DOUBLE
~z~Clay, man, I think it's wise for us to stay together. Can you round up Terrence and get over here?
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~Clay，哥们。我觉得咱们最好待在一起。你能叫上Terrence再过来吗？

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~If the Chapter President wants backup, that's what he'll get.
~z~Clayton, I'd like to ride an Innovation. Can that be arranged?
E1FCC4_ACT_CALL_REQ_SPEC_NOA
~z~Thanks, man.
~z~Dude, how goes it? I'd really like a Revenant if you got time on your hands.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~老兄，最近怎样？如果你现在有空的话，我想要辆Revenant。

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Alright Road Captain. I'd like you to get me a Double. Can you do it?
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~好了行车长，我想要一辆Double。能办到不？

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~Road Captain Clay. Can you bring me a Lycan?
~z~Hey brother. You got any rice rockets over there? Maybe a Hakuchou?
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~嘿，兄弟。有没有亚洲小跑车？比如说Hakuchou？

E1FCC4A.original: ~z~You don't need to be no lone wolf biker, man. Me and Terry are coming.
E1FCC4A.translated: ~z~你不再是孤狼骑手了，哥们。我和Terry在路上了。
